1. *Problema* mi je velika jer nemam dovoljno novca. (The problem is big for me because I don't have enough money.)
2. Uvek ima *problematičnih* ljudi. (There are always problematic people.)
3. Kako rešiti *problematiku* koju imamo? (How to solve the problem we have?)
4. *Problema* je rešena. (The problem is solved.)
5. Moramo razmatrati *problematična* pitanja. (We have to consider problematic questions.)
6. Moramo se potruditi da rešimo *probleme* koje imamo. (We need to work hard to solve the problems we have.)